```class Solution {
    public int maxValue(int n, int index, int maxSum) {
        int left = 1, right = maxSum;
        while (left < right) {
            int mid = (left + right) / 2;
            int sum = 0, prev = 0;
            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                sum += Math.min(mid, prev + 1);
                prev = Math.max(0, prev + 1 - 1);
            }
            if (sum > maxSum) {
                right = mid;
            } else {
                left = mid + 1;
            }
        }
        int sum = 0, prev = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            sum += Math.min(left, prev + 1);
            prev = Math.max(0, prev + 1 - 1);
        }
        return left;
    }
}```
